    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "[Here's an installer](https://seacloud.cc/d/5d1adbebce/files/?p=/OpenRA-release-20150614-with-dir-fix.exe) with a proposed fix for this (see diff below). It's compatible with our current stable release. It would be nice if someone on Windows could\n1. reproduce the bug\n2. confirm that the bug is fixed with the linked installer\n\n``` diff\ndiff --git a/OpenRA.GameMonitor/GameMonitor.cs b/OpenRA.GameMonitor/GameMonitor.cs\nindex bbf9c74..8d648ee 100644\n--- a/OpenRA.GameMonitor/GameMonitor.cs\n+++ b/OpenRA.GameMonitor/GameMonitor.cs\n@@ -28,6 +28,8 @@ static void Main(string[] args)\n                        var executableDirectory = Path.GetDirectoryName(Assembly.GetExecutingAssembly().Location);\n                        var processName = Path.Combine(executableDirectory, \"OpenRA.Game.exe\");\n\n+                       Directory.SetCurrentDirectory(executableDirectory);\n+\n                        var psi = new ProcessStartInfo(processName, string.Join(\" \", args));\n\n                        try\n```\n"
